{
  "stem": "5639.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From, I'll say on the safe side, it would be 1941, at the beginning, till the liquidation of the factory, which was in June, '44.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And by that time, Alfred Rossner was arrested.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They, they arrested him because-- you see, the culture of those times, being inside or outside of ghetto, had one principle, bribe.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "German were the-- Germans were the most bribable people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You could bribe them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Any echelon.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There's no-",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Look, the German who were accessible, if you didn't have directly an access to the upper echelon, you started to bribe on the lower level till your bribe came up to the upper echelon.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A mere mortal couldn't go up to the chief of Gestapo and say, I give you a bottle of whiskey, and don't put my name on the next transport.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You couldn't do that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So, on our behalf, so to say, Rossner was doing the bribing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "His factory depended on government orders.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And government was SS.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And SS actually employed him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because he showed them a true, human, and humane interest.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He spoke Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know much about his background, but I think that he came from a town, and he worked for Jewish families who had factories there, and they actually brought him to Bedzin.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He also, politically, was on the left.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, with all things combined, and there could have been, even, a love story in his life with a Jewish girl.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I am not quite familiar about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Jews from Bedzin who brought him were of German-- were one of the German refugees.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when they brought him here, they knew his abilities.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A, that he's dedicated friend of Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Definitely not a Nazi.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then, that he has got the skills of organizing.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
